README
	This is a game created as a project in the course TDP005 at Linköping University, 2012	

AUTHORS
	This game is created by Thomas Henriksson and Hannah Börjesson

INSTALL
	Requirements for this game to run on Ubuntu:
		SDL 		libsdl1.2-dev
		SDL_image 	libsdl-image1.2-dev
		SDL_ttf 	libsdl-ttf1.2-dev
		g++ 		with support for c++11
		make

How to compile the game:
	Run makefile in the game folder


HOW-TO PLAY
	Compile the game and run 'the_game'.
	
	This is a co-op game. 
	To move player one use keys 'a','d' and 'w'.
	To move player two use arrowkeys left, right and up.
	When standing on the yellow zone all the clouds changes state.
	To win the game or continue to next level both players must stand on a green zone.




